A vintage-style illustration depicting a grumpy orange tabby cat sitting atop a towering stack of weathered technical blueprints and scrolling paper documents, while a determined golden retriever wearing round spectacles attempts to organize scattered mechanical gears, fountain pens, and architectural drafting tools below. The scene is set in a warm, sepia-toned workshop with antique wooden filing cabinets, brass instruments, and ornate Victorian machinery in the background. Dust motes float in shafts of amber light streaming through a mullioned window. The cat's tail drapes lazily over flowing documents covered in intricate technical diagrams and flowcharts, while the dog methodically sorts papers into neat piles. The atmosphere conveys both tension and reluctant cooperation between chaos and order.
